29a3 xda h6 y1507 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">then the line of distinction will be </div><div class="t m5 x5c h6 y239 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t mc58 x8f h6 y13db ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing the sign of submission to earthly </div><div class="t mc36 xda h6 y14ce ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">drawn between those who serve God powers, receive the mark of the beast, </div><div class="t m5 x93 h6 y2ca4 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"></span></div><div class="t m526 xda h6 y1fd4 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and those who serve Him not. While the </div><div class="t m5 x5c h6 y30a ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m1608 x90 h6 y1fd4 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the other, choosing the token of alle- </div><div class="t m5 x93 h6 y2ca4 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"></span></div><div class="t m167d xc4 h6 y1608 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">observance of the false sabbath in com- </div><div class="t m5 x5c h6 y32a ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t mba6 x90 h6 y1608 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">giance to divine authority, receive the </div><div class="t m5 x93 h6 y2ca4 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"></span></div><div class="t m158f xc4 h6 y14fd ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pliance with the law of the state, con- </div><div class="t m5 x5c h6 y39 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m3b6 x8f h6 y14fd ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seal of God.&quot;—&quot;The Great Controversy,&quot; </div><div class="t m5 x93 h6 y2ca4 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"></span></div><div class="t m105b xc4 h6 y14d2 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trary to the fourth commandment, will </div><div class="t m5 x5c h6 y13ed ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m1c8d x90 h6 y14d2 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 605. </div><div class="t m191 xc4 h6 y1f97 ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be an avowal of allegiance to a power </div><div class="t m736 xc4 h6 y11ce ff2 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FOR FURTHER STUDY: &quot;The Great Contro